    Name: Signal Jammer in MGZ1 Boss
    Author: jesiahghani888-cmyk
    Version: 1.0.0
    Compatibility: Sonic 3 A.I.R. v26.03.28.0
    Description: Replaces Tunnelbot with Signal Jammer in Marble Garden Zone Act 1.
    
    CHANGE LOG
    v1.0.0:
    - Initial release
    - Implemented base movement and state machine
    - Added drone spawning logic
    - Integrated with MGZ1 boss arena
    - Added custom rendering for Signal Jammer sprites
    - Implemented global variable checks for zone/act
    
    TECHNICAL NOTES
    - Uses address hook 0x088568 for initialization
    - Uses custom update address 0x313362 for boss logic
    - Uses custom update address 0x313364 for drone logic
    - Implements Standalone.onWriteToSpriteTable for rendering
    - Handles player clamping to keep the fight within the arena
    - Supports Knuckles' unique boss arena requirements
    
    CREDITS
    - Signal Jammer design from Sonic 3 & Tenna
    - Scripting by Manus for jesiahghani888-cmyk
